nce of these contracts is enormous since they form the connection between producers and retailers who sell the products to consumers and other final users. There are only very few economic sectors where producers regularly sell their products directly to final consumer users.Goodwill compensation after the ending of a distribution contract, the moment at which the agent's commission is due, the franchisor's obligation to maintain the good reputation of the network are but a few examples of issues where specific rules are needed in order to give legal practice some guidance and to provide practitioners with a reasonable degree of legal certainty.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 28. Feb 2023) 0aCivil law -- European Union countries. 0aCivil lawzEuropean Union countries. 7aLAW / International.2bisacsh1 aBueno Diaz, Odavia, eauthor.4aut4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/aut1 aRutgers, Jacobien W., eauthor.4aut4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/aut1 aScotton, Manolo, eauthor.4aut4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/aut1 aVeldman, Muriel, eauthor.4aut4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/aut08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertDGBA Backlist Complete English Language 2000-2014 PART1z978311023857008iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertDGBA Backlist History 2000-2014 (EN)z978311062100608iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertDGBA Law - 2000 - 2014z9783110636208oZDB-23-GLA08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertE-BOOK GESAMTPAKET / COMPLETE PACKAGE 2009z9783110219517oZDB-23-DGG08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertE-BOOK PACKAGE ENGLISH LANGUAGES TITLES 2009z978311021952408iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertE-BOOK PAKET RECHTSWISSENSCHAFTEN 2009z9783899496871oZDB-23-DGC40uhttps://doi.org/10.1515/978386653707140uhttps://www.degruy